# {{.ProjectName}} Agent Notes

Use `plugin.yaml` and `targets/cursor/**` as the repo-owned source of truth for Cursor workspace config.

When updating Cursor integration:

- prefer editing `targets/cursor/rules/**` over hand-editing `.cursor/rules/**`
- prefer editing `mcp/servers.json` over hand-editing `.cursor/mcp.json`
- run `plugin-kit-ai render .` and `plugin-kit-ai validate . --platform cursor --strict` after changes
